
Broadcom Mini Driver Kit (MDK)
==============================

The Broadcom MDK provides a basic programming interface and a basic
API for Broadcom network switch devices.

Package Contents
----------------

The MDK contains the following directories/components:

cdk   - Chip Development Kit
bmd   - Broadcom Mini Driver API
phy   - PHY driver Library
board - Board specific code/drivers
doc   - Documentation

Please refer to the documentation in the doc directory for a detailed
description of the MDK components and build instructions for the
sample applications.

